Package: mscgeometR
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for Querying the Meteorological Service of Canada’s (MSC) 'GeoMet' webservices
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(person("Ryan", "Whaley", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "rdgwhaley@gmail.com"))
Description: R wrapper for querying the Meteorological Service of Canada’s (MSC) GeoMet webservices. Includes functionality for querying both 
  the GeoMet Web Coverage Service (WCS) as well as the OGC OpenAPI endpoint.
  For more information on both services, please see the official documentation (<https://eccc-msc.github.io/open-data/msc-geomet/web-services_en/>).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
  R (>= 4.2.0)
Suggests: 
    raster,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    httr2,
    purrr,
    tibble,
    vctrs,
    xml2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
